description:
Anya Dostoyevskaya is a Single Undine working in http://anidb.net/ch125950 [Orange Planet] and http://anidb.net/ch8499 [Alice]`s junior. She has a calm and gentle personality, but sometimes demonstrates spontaneity, such as blurting out "From Siberia!" to anyone she has just met. She sometimes speaks in a literary tone. She practices with http://anidb.net/ch75708 [Azusa] from http://anidb.net/ch125951 [Himeya].
Source: ANN
